### Component 6: `ForecastGrid` (4-col)

**Source in scaffolding:** `MACRO_PRESIGNALS` hardcoded array → `MacroSnapshotCard`
**Replace with:** `buildForecastCards(data: MasterBrief): ForecastCard[]` helper

```ts
function buildForecastCards(data: MasterBrief): ForecastCard[] {
  return [
    { slug: 'cpi-now',   label: 'PRE SIGNAL', title: 'CPI Now',   actual: data.nowcast.cpi_mom + '%',           cons: '0.3%',  delta: ..., bias: ... },
    { slug: 'pce-now',   label: 'PRE SIGNAL', title: 'Core PCE',  actual: data.nowcast.core_pce_mom + '%',      cons: '0.3%',  delta: ..., bias: ... },
    { slug: 'adp-miss',  label: 'ADP',        title: 'ADP Emp',   actual: data.adp_prediction.prediction + '',  cons: ...,     delta: ..., bias: data.adp_prediction.signal },
    { slug: 'gdp-miss',  label: 'GDP',        title: 'GDP Q1',    actual: data.gdp_nowcast.gdp_estimate + '%',  cons: ...,     delta: ..., bias: data.gdp_nowcast.signal },
  ].filter(c => c.actual !== 'null%' && c.actual !== 'undefined%');
}
```

